NodeComment: Simple Arithmetic has 4 grammars which are "Digit", "Number", "Expr", and "Equation" described below.

This module implements a formal system named "Simple Arithmetic". It aims to be the first example of formal system for new comer to play around. Please note that this is just a faction of actual arithmetic modified to make it easy to understand, so it is not as powerful as the actual one.\n\nFor further information, please see chapter 3 (Background) and chapter 4 (Example - Simple Arithmetic) in phometa documentation.
Simple Arithmetic has several rules explained below. Please note that these are not exhaustive, it only aims to explain basic feature of phometa.
